<div id="column1" class="box box_scroll">
<H1>Open Water Events</H1>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://greatswim.org/" target="newwindow"> Great Swim</a> Great Swim is home to mass participation open water swimming events.
<li><a href="http://www.oceanswims.com/" target="newwindow">Ocean Swims</a> Includes worldwide event details and contact information.
<li><img src="images/logos/logo_triangle.jpg" width="100" height="38" hspace="3" align="left" /><a href="http://www.triangleopenwater.com/" target="newwindow">Triangle Open Water</a> Triangle Open Water Swim series consists of three one-mile open water swimming events located in North Carolina.
<li><a href="http://www.nycswim.org/" target="newwindow">NYC Swim</a> Sponsors of the Manhattan Island Marathon Swim, Great Hudson River Swim, Little Red Lighthouse Swim and the Wrong Way Swim. Collection of articles related to open water swimming, training tips, and information on braving the English Channel.
<li><a href="http://www.swimtrek.com" target="newwindow">SwimTrek</a> Features open water swimming adventure holidays to the Mediterranean, Caribbean, Middle East & Northern Europe.
<li><a href="http://usopenwaterswimming.org/" target="newwindow">U.S. Open Water Swimming</a> Open Water Swimming Information Including Race Schedule and places to swim.
<li><a href="http://www.10kswim.com/mainMenu.html" target="newwindow">10KSwim</a> A comprehensive graphic description of and informaton on the newest sport at the Olympics.
<li><a href="http://www.bayswim.com/" target="newwindow">Great Chesapeake Bay Swim </a> The 4.4 Mile swim near Annapolis is considered one of the most sought after open water swims in the U.S.
<li><a href="http://www.pacificswims.com/" target="newwindow">Pacific Ocean Swims</a> Organises and promotes ocean swims in the Pacific region. Information on ocean swimming events worldwide.
<li><img src="images/logos/logo_sri_chinmoy.jpg" width="250" height="40" /><br/>
<a href="http://www.srichinmoyraces.org/channel" target="newwindow">Sri Chinmoy Channel Swimmers</a> Members of the Sri Chinmoy Marathon Team have made over forty Channel Crossings.
<li><a href="http://www.traversee.qc.ca/index.php?id=1&lang=eng" target="newwindow">Lake Saint-Jean International Swimming Marathon </a> Annual 32 kilometer swim from Pi√©kouagami to Roberval in Quebec, Canada.
<li><a href="http://www.rcptiburonmile.com/" target="newwindow"> RCP Tiburon Mile Open Water Swim</a> The World's Premiere International Open Water Swim.
<li><a href="http://www.capeswim.com/" target="newwindow"> Open Water Swimming in Cape Town</a>Website offers information and news on open water swimming in Cape Town.
<li><a href="http://www.channelswimmingassociation.com/" target="newwindow">Channel Swimming Association</a> Are you interested in long distance open water swimming? Are you thinking of swimming the English Channel? This website gives you all the information you need to know how you can do it.
<li><a href="http://www.bigshoulders.org/" target="newwindow">Big Shoulders 5K swim</a> The Big Shoulders 5K Swim: a Lake Michigan-size test of guts, determination and fortitude amidst the chilly, windswept waves.
<li><a href="http://www.rottnestchannelswim.com.au/" target="newwindow">Rottnest Channel Swim Association</a> The purpose of the association is to promote and conduct the annual Rottnest Channel Swim.
<li><a href="http://www.armyopenwaterswimming.co.uk/" target="newwindow">Army Open Water Swimming</a> The home of the British Army open water swimming.</a>
<li><a href="http://www.pacificopenwater.com/" target="newwindow">Pacific Open Water</a> Events include a 5K open water swim, a 1 mile open water swim, 1/2 mile open water swim.
<li><a href="http://www.thebigswim.org.au/" target="newwindow">The Big Swim</a> The course runs for about 2.7 km from Palm Beach to  Whale Beach.
</li>
</ul>
